description:
This is a 33 minute workout called 'Standing Cardio Workout | No Jumping | Includes Warm Up and Cool Down Stretch | 30 Minutes' from the channel The Girl With The Pilates Mat.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Standing Cardio Workout | No Jumping | Includes Warm Up and Cool Down Stretch | 30 Minutes

Join me for a 30 minute standing pilates cardio workout. This will help you lose weight, gain muscle tone and improve your cardiovascular health.  Safe for the joints as no jumping, this session is a fun workout targeting the whole body to boost your metabolism and give you a really good full body pilates workout. It will be a challenge so be prepared to get a little sweaty! 

Do check out my other high energy workouts here:
